{"type": "article", "id": 31028, "title": "以色列这个住宅，到处都是纤细的线条和清淡的颜色", "description": "像这个案例，就是用精致的黑色框架打磨出的高级感。", "date": "2016-08-15T23:12:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 14006, "name": "住宅设计"}, {"id": 15294, "name": "老房改造"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 510, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160815215059xgdisrUMBvOLQtmf.jpg", "contents": "<p>用清晰有力的线条和低彩度色调表达直观性的审美，是很多极简主义风格的住宅标志性的特点。</p><p>这种讲求单纯理性的室内空间，适合那些在设计上偏好干净利落线条，不喜欢太多无谓装饰的屋主。最近，在以色列特拉维夫，一处老旧公寓的改造项目，称得上是以这种风格作为整体设计基调的良好注解。</p><p>创造这一空间的是室内设计师 Maayan Zusman 和建筑师 Amir Navon。</p><p>想要精准把控极简风，在讲求简单纯粹美感的同时，在施工品质上丝毫都马虎不得。像这个案例，就是用精致的黑色框架打磨出的高级感。95 平方米的开放式公寓包括起居空间、厨房用餐空间以及各配有一间独立浴室的卧室。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215213krlnPcfF4ISMRgmp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">卧室一</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215213p62ymd4aRugIt7eH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">卧室二</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215242bZK8Xut6pqvxwWia.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215242NGREVLhuM3o9tS46.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">浴室</div></figcaption></figure></div><p>从门框到窗框，从定制家具到空间隔断，设计师对于这些黑色框架的使用，好似在创作一幅素描作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215317OJmKVUMXFGS2yBHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215317PhXgwjFu3fy7HokN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>它既是引导人们视线在各个空间游移的线索，也扮演定义不同功能区域的角色。最突破想象力的使用方式呈现在起居空间，一根“顶天立地”的黑色细圆柱变身成为挂置壁挂式电视机的地方，省去了摆放电视柜的空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215333JouvjGMixZXzeTCy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>就连悬挂于餐桌上方的意大利顶级灯饰品牌 Flos 的黑色线状吊灯，也呼应了黑色框架的主题元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215350flL8cvCNdbr3KRuh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>另有卫浴空间用来放置水槽和卫浴用品的置物架，以及起居室的定制金属书架，都延续了黑色框架主题。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215408yLQ2NaPcYkp0gWhs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215409GvDhW9lASEdLRz0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">“我们希望为公寓开辟尽可能敞亮、通风的空间。” <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/08/14/maayan-zusman-renovation-tel-aviv-apartment-interior-design-thin-black-frames/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maayan Zusman 表示</a>。<br></p><p>为了保持空间在视觉上尽可能地清爽简洁，淡淡的豆绿色橱柜将冰箱等包裹在内，除了创造了大体量的存储空间之外，还内嵌了一个带有书桌的工作区小角落。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081521545157VXMd2PERGxLFzN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608152154519N6JwZYQo1jsL78U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215451I7R3ZP0rUHYOzlGA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215451r2acmVN3HDdQz7hX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>如果不是特别留意的话，你大概会以为这是一个由混凝土铺贴的地面，但实际上用的却是环氧树脂材料。Maayan Zusman 将其描述为<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/08/14/maayan-zusman-renovation-tel-aviv-apartment-interior-design-thin-black-frames/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“极其平稳且适合行走”</a>的地板材料，<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/08/14/maayan-zusman-renovation-tel-aviv-apartment-interior-design-thin-black-frames/\" rel=\"nofollow\">她说</a>：“我们想创造的，是没有任何边缘切割痕迹的地板风格，呈现出光滑干净的样子。”</p><p>而在极简的基调之下，少数几个跳出来的个性化元素则显得活泼、醒目，比如选自意大利顶级家居品牌 Boffi 的浴室红色花朵状水龙头，以及挂于起居室墙面有如雕塑艺术般表现形式的蓝色挂钟。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215520cOqdV7sEoWtMYrnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215520Mc5RwvrqCiPdguG7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815215520hlQMngORyuf2W5EH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/08/14/maayan-zusman-renovation-tel-aviv-apartment-interior-design-thin-black-frames/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a> 摄影：181</p>"}